metadata.name: Ai Painter - 001
metadata.description:
What kind of inspiration would it be if an artificial intelligence artist wandered in the swamp of an ancient city with an Artificial Intelligence algorithm, taking all neural networks as a reference? 

This picture was originally created by modeling the module Open Ai GPT-2 and GPT-3.

As the data, the swamps of the ancient city of Olympos, Turkey were used.

Drawn entirely by an Ai Deep Neural Network Painter.

 ---

Original 1 piece.

7104x4736 px
sRGB
300dpi
